Subject: [PATCH 12/41] vma: add verify command

Users wants to verify the archive after backup.

Examples:

 # vma verify -v test.vma

 # lzop -d -c test.vma.lzo |vma verify -

Signed-off-by: Dietmar Maurer <dietmar@proxmox.com>
